<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Horaires de prière</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="google" content="notranslate">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">

        {% stylesheets 
            "bundles/app/bootstrap-3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            filter="cssrewrite"
        %}
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset_url }}" type="text/css">
        {% endstylesheets %}

        <link media="screen and (min-width: 1200px)" href="/bundles/app/prayer-times/css/desktop.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link media="screen and (max-width: 1200px)" href="/bundles/app/prayer-times/css/mobile.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link media="screen and (min-width: 1200px)" href="/bundles/app/prayer-times/css/douaa-slider.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico" />
    </head>
    <body class="text-center">
        <div class="desktop hidden-xs hidden-sm hidden-md">
            <div class="spinner"></div>

            <!-- Iqama screen -->
            <div class="iqama hidden">
                <div class="top">{{'iqama'|trans}}</div>
                <div class="image"></div>
                <div class="bottom">{{'power-off-phones'|trans}}</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Douaa after prayer slider -->
            <div class="douaa-after-prayer display-none">
                {% if mosque.configuration.smallScreen  %}
                    {% include 'partial/dua-slider.html.twig' %}
                {% else %}
                    {% include 'partial/dua-slider-one-screen.html.twig' %}
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <!-- Adhan screen -->
            <div class="adhan display-none">
                <div class="ar">
                    <div class="title">دعاء ما بعد الأذان</div>
                    اللّهُـمَّ رَبَّ هَذِهِ الدّعْـوَةِ التّـامَّة وَالصّلاةِ القَـائِمَة آتِ محَـمَّداً الوَسيـلةَ وَالْفَضـيلَة وَابْعَـثْه مَقـامـاً مَحـموداً الَّذي وَعَـدْتَه 
                </div>

                <div class="fr">
                    <div class="title">Invocation après l'adhân</div>
                    Ô Allah, Maître de cet appel parfait et de la prière que l'on va accomplir, donne à Mohammed le pouvoir d'intercéder 
                    (le Jour du Jugement) et la place d'honneur [au Paradis], et ressuscite-le dans la position louable que Tu lui as promise
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="douaa-between-adhan-iqama display-none">
                <div class="ar">
                    <div class="title">الدعاء لا يرد بين الأذان والإقامة</div>
                    عَنْ أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ: الدُّعَاءُ لَا يُرَدُّ بَيْنَ الْأَذَانِ وَالْإِقَامَةِ
                </div>

                <div class="fr">
                    <div class="title">Les invocations entre le Adhân et l’Iqâmah ne sont pas rejetées</div>
                    Selon Anas Ibn Mâlik, le Prophète (sallallahu ‘alayhi wa sallam) a dit : « Les invocations entre le Adhân et l’Iqâmah ne sont pas rejetées»
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- main screen -->
            <div class="main display-none">
                <div class="header">{{mosque.name}} - {{mosque.city}}</div> 

                <div class="top-content">
                    <div class="adhan-flash hidden">
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-8">
                            <span>{{'azan'|trans}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" style="transform: scaleX(-1);">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="col-lg-3 aid custom-time">
                            <div>{{'aid'|trans}}</div>
                            <div class="aid-id"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 chourouk custom-time">
                            <div>{{'shuruk'|trans}}</div>
                            <div class="chourouk-id"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 imsak custom-time">
                            <div>{{'imsak'|trans}}</div>
                            <div class="imsak-id"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="time"></div>
                            <div class="hijriDate"></div>
                            <div class="gregorianDate"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class=" col-lg-3 joumouaa">
                            <div>{{'jumua'|trans}}</div>
                            <div class="prayer joumouaa-id"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="prayer-content">
                    <div class="prayer-text">
                        <div class="text _0">{{'fajr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="text _1">{{'zuhr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="text _2">{{'asr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="text _3">{{'maghrib'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="text _4">{{'isha'|trans}}</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="prayer-time">
                        <div class="sobh prayer"></div>
                        <div class="dohr prayer"></div>
                        <div class="asr prayer"></div>
                        <div class="maghrib prayer"></div>
                        <div class="ichaa prayer"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="prayer-wait">
                        <div class="wait _0"></div>
                        <div class="wait _1"></div>
                        <div class="wait _2"></div>
                        <div class="wait _3"></div>
                        <div class="wait _4"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="footer">
                    <div class="col-lg-1 text-center android-app visibilty-hidden">
                        <span>App Android</span>
                        <img class="app-qr-code" src="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-10">
                        <div class="site">{{site|raw}}</div>
                        <div class="assosciation">
                            {{'association_info'|trans({'%name%': mosque.associationName, '%phone%': mosque.phone})}}
                            {{ mosque.rib is not empty ? 'rib_info'|trans({'%rib%': mosque.rib}) : '' }}
                        </div>
                        <div class="support">
                            <span>{{'support'|trans}}</span> 
                            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone"></i> <a href="tel:{{supportTel}}" class="supportTel">{{supportTel}}</a>&nbsp;
                            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="supportEmail">{{supportEmail}}</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-1 version-parent">
                        <span class="version fr">v{{version}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mobile hidden-lg">
            <div class="spinner"></div>

            <div class="main display-none">
                <div class="header">{{mosque.name}} - {{mosque.city}}</div>
                <div class="top-content">
                    <div class="time"></div>
                    <div class="hijriDate ar"></div>
                    <div class="gregorianDate"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="prayer-content">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 text">{{'fajr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer prayer0 sobh"></div> 
                        <div class="col-xs-4 adhan0 hidden">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" class="athan-img">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 wait"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 text">{{'zuhr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer prayer1 dohr"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 adhan1 hidden">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" class="athan-img">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 wait"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 text">{{'asr'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer prayer2 asr"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 adhan2 hidden">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" class="athan-img">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 wait"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 text">{{'maghrib'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer prayer3 maghrib"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 adhan3 hidden">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" class="athan-img">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 wait"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 text">{{'isha'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer prayer4 ichaa"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 adhan4 hidden">
                            <img src="{{asset('bundles/app/prayer-times/img/loudspeaker.png')}}" class="athan-img">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 wait"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="chourouk-joumouaa">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-1 imsak custom-time">{{'imsak'|trans}}</div> 
                        <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-1 chourouk custom-time">{{'shuruk'|trans}}</div> 
                        <div class="col-xs-2"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 joumouaa">{{'jumua'|trans}}</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-1"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-1 imsak custom-time imsak-id"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-1 chourouk custom-time chourouk-id "></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4 prayer joumouaa-id"></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-1"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="footer">
                    <div class="assosciation text-center">
                        {{'association_info'|trans({'%name%': mosque.associationName, '%phone%': mosque.phone})}}
                        {{ mosque.rib is not empty ? 'rib_info'|trans({'%rib%': mosque.rib}) : '' }}
                    </div>
                    <div class="support">
                        <span>{{'support'|trans}}</span> : <br>
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone"></i> <a href="tel:{{supportTel}}" class="supportTel">{{supportTel}}</a>&nbsp;
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="supportEmail">{{supportEmail}}</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="version text-right">v{{version}}</div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            var confData = {{config|raw}};
            var lang = "{{lang}}";
        </script>

        {% javascripts
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/jquery/js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/bootstrap-3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/vendor/jquery.countdown.min.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/vendor/hijriDate.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/vendor/PrayTimes.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/tools.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/date.js'
                '@AppBundle/Resources/public/prayer-times/js/prayer.js'
        %}
        <script src="{{ asset_url }}"></script>
        {% endjavascripts %}    
    </body>
</html>